-- Accentuate in Venture With Water Treatment Company Ion Exchange
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2012-06-19T12:27:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-19/accentuate-in-venture-with-water-treatment-company-ion-exchange.html
Accentuate Ltd. (ACE)  said its Safic (Pty)
Ltd. unit concluded a joint venture agreement with Ion Exchange
(India) Ltd. to widen its water treatment operations in  South
Africa .  Under terms of the accord that are effective July 1, the
venture’s ownership of Ion Exchange-Safic (Pty) Ltd. will be 60
percent held by Ion and the remainder by Safic. The venture will
be established in Johannesburg with offices operating from
Accentuate’s site in Steeldale, the company said in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
